Google began as a research project in January 1996 by Larry Page and Sergey Brin, two [[Doctor of Philosophy|Ph.D.]] students at [[Stanford University]], [[California]].<ref name="milestones">"[http://www.google.com/intl/en/corporate/history.html Corporate Information: Google Milestones]." "[http://dbpubs.stanford.edu:8090/pub/1999-66 The PageRank Citation Ranking: Bringing Order to the Web]."
